race.comment: TENNESSEE KADE (5) unbeaten in two runs so far and shows good promise. Two of her wins have been this trip. Can measure up again. ROCKY SUPERSTAR (1) has been in super consistent form recently with four minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing seventh (25.58) at this track. Leading chance. ZIPPING DARGAN (2) is having his first start around this track. In the money last start when second (26.41) at Geelong over 460m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Deserves a win and gets his chance. RATTLER (3) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.
